Treat your little one to the sweet taste of real apple with Full Cheeks Apple Slices. Made with love for rabbits, guinea pigs, and most small animals, these treats are made with 100% real apple your small pet will love. All they need to do is what they do best: give lots of love. Only at PetSmart.
